ussr.physics
Class PhysicsParameters

java.lang.Object
  ussr.physics.PhysicsParameters

public class PhysicsParameters
extends java.lang.Object

A collection of parameters that describe the physical properties of the simulation. [Currently] implemented as a singleton. Some parameters a default value (step size, gravity, etc.) whereas other parameters are optional and only have a value after the have been set. The parameters are to some extent specific to the JME physics engine (which again is based on ODE).

Author:
Modular Robots @ MMMI
